  "3269050": {
    "name": "The Lost Hunter",
    "steam_appid": 3269050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>子弹--时间效应：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/26770929fe5a5f6ddbd07098724f75a9.poster.avif?t=1772480592\" width=800 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/26770929fe5a5f6ddbd07098724f75a9.webm?t=1772480592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞄准目标，扣动扳机，一刻不停地追踪子弹的轨迹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >得益于我们游戏中的子弹追踪效果，您可以详细追踪每一发子弹的威力和冲击力。无论是在广袤的林地还是开阔的田野，通过跟踪每一颗子弹到达目标的过程，您的狩猎体验将更上一层楼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这项功能让每一瞬间都更具战略性，更令人兴奋。现在就看您的狙击技巧能否击中目标了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>工艺系统：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/369d1aeeba88fbfdeb5448e2d6428bea.poster.avif?t=1772480592\" width=800 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/369d1aeeba88fbfdeb5448e2d6428bea.webm?t=1772480592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您不仅要猎杀猎物，还要将其加工成宝贵的资源！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您不仅可以从猎物身上获取肉类，还可以收集皮革和其他材料，用于制作工艺品。您可以安营扎寨，生火烹饪采集到的肉类，还可以自己准备食物，考验自己的生存技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但狩猎仅仅是个开始！利用获得的材料，您可以制作新装备、改进武器或巩固营地。您还可以砍伐木材，获取宝贵的贸易资源，并利用手工机制制作新物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大自然为您提供了生存所需的一切，关键是您要知道如何利用它！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>鹰追踪系统：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/79536bb137c9b8b0351409167ddcec6b.poster.avif?t=1772480592\" width=800 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/79536bb137c9b8b0351409167ddcec6b.webm?t=1772480592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您忠实的朋友，您的护身符老鹰，将是您在狩猎冒险中的最大帮手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这只神秘而强大的鹰将在天空中搜寻猎物，并在狩猎过程中指引你。当您迷失方向或危险临近时，它将始终陪伴在您身边。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它敏锐的眼睛会让您更容易发现猎物并制定策略。与老鹰之间的这种独特纽带将使您的狩猎不仅充满技巧，还充满直觉和自然的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>能量饮料 - 睡眠机械：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/f8285d43282faea2003ed31a2fa5018b.poster.avif?t=1772480592\" width=800 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/f8285d43282faea2003ed31a2fa5018b.webm?t=1772480592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了生存，使用正确的补充剂与休息同样重要！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在某些时候，您的角色可以通过睡觉或饮用能量饮料来补充能量。但是，您必须小心，夜幕降临时，自然界会变得更加危险。睡觉和饮用能量饮料需要您就如何度过夜晚做出战略性决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你选择不睡觉，能量饮料可以让你坚持下去，但从长远来看，这会使你的免疫力下降。如果您生病或受伤，抗生素将是确保您生存的最重要资源之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>射击范围:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/b5893b5cab0702dad79b89318db4bed8.poster.avif?t=1772480592\" width=800 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/b5893b5cab0702dad79b89318db4bed8.webm?t=1772480592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过我们游戏中特有的射击场系统，您可以测试并提高自己的射击技能。这个区域配备了不同的距离和目标，为提高您的瞄准技能提供了理想的环境。凭借敏锐的反应和正确的策略掌握射击技巧，为真正的狩猎冒险做好准备！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>贸易技工：</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/0cb34614ea082e1c1d9acd16518cf845.poster.avif?t=1772480592\" width=800 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269050/extras/0cb34614ea082e1c1d9acd16518cf845.webm?t=1772480592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以通过向特定时间营业的商人出售肉、皮和骨头等资源来赚取狩猎收入。交易是增加生存机会的最重要途径之一。您可以用赚来的钱购买交易商提供的装备，提高狩猎和生存的效率。不过，交易商并不总是开门营业，因此您应该把握好交易时间，战略性地使用资源。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 印地语, 瑞典语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
